FF Description: The conic sections are formed by taking
flat slices of a solid double right cone.
You can generate them with a lamp and shade!

<P>
Take any lamp with a cylindrical shade and observe
the light cone's projection on the wall!
<BR>
Put it next to the wall (hyperbola).
<BR>
Tilt (parabola).
<BR>
Tilt more (ellipse).
<BR>
Align horizontal (circle).




Presentation suggestions: Make shadow puppets just to be funny.



